# Design System Profile: Text Convertor

This document provides a structured, machine-readable guide to the visual and UX standards for the 'Text Convertor' project. It is derived from the "Technology & Product Strategy Memorandum" and the V1 MVP Svelte component implementation.

## 1. Design Philosophy

The core design philosophy is one of **extreme minimalism and focus**. The user interface must be clean, intuitive, and designed to remove all friction from the user's workflow. The design is **mobile-first**, ensuring a seamless and accessible experience on any device.

## 2. Layout System

The application uses a responsive layout that adapts to the viewport width.

* **Mobile (Default, < 768px):** A single-column, vertical layout where the "Input" area is stacked above the "Output" area.
* **Desktop (> 768px):** A two-column, side-by-side layout that provides a real-time conversion view, with the "Input" on the left and "Output" on the right.

## 3. Colour Palette

The palette is restrained to support the minimalist and utilitarian aesthetic.

| Element          | Property           | Value    |
| :--------------- | :----------------- | :------- |
| `textarea`       | `border-color`     | `#ccc`   |
| `.output-area`   | `background-color` | `#f8f9fa` |
| `.output-area`   | `color`            | `#333`   |
| `.btn-primary`   | `background-color` | `#007bff` |
| `.btn-primary`   | `color`            | `white`  |
| `.btn-secondary` | `background-color` | `#6c757d` |
| `.btn-secondary` | `color`            | `white`  |
| `.copy-feedback` | `color`            | `#28a745` |

## 4. Typography

Typography is standardized for clarity and readability.

* **Primary Font Family:** `monospace`
* **Base Font Size:** `14px`

## 5. Component Styles

### `textarea` (shared style `.text-area`)

* **Border:** `1px solid #ccc`
* **Border Radius:** `8px`
* **Padding:** `0.75rem`
* **Sizing:** `width: 100%`, `height: 100%`, `box-sizing: border-box`
* **Resize:** `none` (disabled)

### Buttons (shared style `.btn`)

* **Padding:** `0.5rem 1rem`
* **Border:** `none`
* **Border Radius:** `6px`
* **Font Weight:** `500`
* **Cursor:** `pointer`
* **Transition:** `background-color 0.2s ease`
* **Primary (`.btn-primary`):** A solid blue background (`#007bff`) with white text.
* **Secondary (`.btn-secondary`):** A solid grey background (`#6c757d`) with white text.

### Feedback Text (`.copy-feedback`)

* **Colour:** Green (`#28a745`)
* **Font Weight:** `bold`

## 6. Microcopy

The following text strings are to be used exactly as specified to ensure a clear and consistent user experience.

* **Page Title:** `Text Convertor | Clean Up Your Text Instantly`
* **Input Placeholder:** `Paste your Markdown, notes, or AI-generated text here...`
* **Output Placeholder:** `Your clean, plain text will appear here.`
* **Primary Button Label:** `Copy Text`
* **Secondary Button Label:** `Clear`
* **Copy Success Feedback:** `Copied!`